## Credentials

Dr Nathan Newman, MD, is a board-certified physician and stem cell scientist with over two decades of research and clinical practice. He is the inventor and patent holder of the foundational **Consortia Factors®** technology platform — a method for production, formulation and use of conditioned media, cultured cells and the bioactive factors contained therein. The platform is the scientific basis for The Stem Company's regenerative skincare products.

Dr Newman has authored peer-reviewed publications spanning more than twenty years, contributed chapters to industry textbooks, and is the author of the 2025 book *The Natural Intelligence of Stem Cells: The Story of a Breakthrough Discovery* (The STEM Company, 2025).

He is a frequent contributor to industry trade press, including *Skin Inc.* and *Global Cosmetic Industry*, and a regular speaker at conferences on stem cell science.

